videos.description: Cincinnati's Kyle Washington gets the ball in the post and shakes of two defenders for the bucket.
videos.headline: Washington drains post jumper

videos.description: After grabbing the rebound on the offensive end, Cincinnati's Jarron Cumberland finds space and nails the 3-pointer.
videos.headline: Cumberland drains 3 after rebound

videos.description: After grabbing the rebound off Justin Jenifer's missed shot, Gary Clark sinks the contested shot in the first half.
videos.headline: Clark earns second-chance bucket

videos.description: After Cincinnati's Jacob Evans gets the steal off the inbound, Florida's Keith Stone comes from behind and rejects the shot attempt.
videos.headline: Stone denies Evans after steal

videos.description: Florida's Chris Chiozza finds Keith Stone open in the corner for the 3-pointer in the first half.
videos.headline: Chiozza sets up Stone's open 3

videos.description: Cincinnati's Cane Broome splits through the Gators' defense and nails the contested layup.
videos.headline: Broome sets up potential 3-point play after tough layup

videos.description: Cincinnati's Jarron Cumberland zips a pass inside to Kyle Washington for the emphatic dunk.
videos.headline: Washington throws down two-handed dunk

videos.description: Cincinnati's Jacob Evans drives down low and drains the contested layup in the first half.
videos.headline: Evans sinks layup for and-1 chance

videos.description: Cincinnati's Cane Broome breezes right by the Gators' defense and sinks the contested layup for a potential 3-point play.
videos.headline: Broome buries contested layup to set up and-1 chance

videos.description: Florida's Chris Chiozza breaks out the jab step before stepping back and sinking the jumper.
videos.headline: Chiozza converts step-back jumper

videos.description: After grabbing the defensive rebound, Florida's Chris Chiozza splits right through the defense and sinks the euro-step layup.
videos.headline: Chiozza nails euro-step layup

videos.description: Florida's Chris Chiozza fires a pass up to Egor Koulechov in transition for the finger roll.
videos.headline: Chiozza finds Koulechov in transition for layup

videos.description: Florida's KeVaughn Allen goes baseline and buries the one-handed floater in the second half.
videos.headline: Allen sinks floater for 3-point chance

videos.description: Cincinnati's Jarron Cumberland heaves a pass from half court to Jacob Evans for the alley-oop layup.
videos.headline: Cumberland's long pass sets up alley-oop

videos.description: After losing his man on the pump fake, Cincinnati's Jarron Cumberland drives down the lane and sinks the tough layup.
videos.headline: Cumberland splits through Gators for hoop and harm

videos.description: Florida's Chris Chiozza swings a pass over to Deaundrae Ballard for the crafty layup in the second half.
videos.headline: Chiozza sets up Ballard's crafty layup

videos.description: With time running out late in the game, Florida's Chris Chiozza creates space and sinks the one-handed jumper.
videos.headline: Chiozza drills go-ahead bucket
